                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <h4 class="title-md-montbold">Challenges Faced by Field Service Businesses to Manage Field Teams</h4>
                    <p class="text-justify">In the field service industry, managing a successful team can be challenging due to various factors. Some of the common challenges faced by service businesses include:</p>
                    <div class="mt-4">
                        <img src="../assets/images/blog/how_to_manage_field_service_team_2.jpg" class="img-fluid">
