                </div>
                 <div class="mt-5">
                    <h4 class="title-md-montbold">1.  Skilled Labor Shortage</h4>
                    <p class="text-justify mb-3">One of the major challenges faced by service businesses is the shortage of skilled labor. Finding and recruiting the right talent with the necessary technical skills and experience can be difficult and time-consuming.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <h4 class="title-md-montbold">2. Employee Retention</h4>
                    <p class="text-justify mb-3">Retaining skilled field service technicians can be challenging, especially in industries with high turnover rates. Service businesses need to provide attractive compensation packages, opportunities for career growth, and a positive work environment to retain their employees</p>
                </div>
